scope (broad orphan disease umbrella, ~7000 known rare diseases):
- congenital genetic disorders (lysosomal storage / metabolic enzyme defects)
- pediatric oncology (cross-link `.roadmap.disease_cancer`)
- pediatric epilepsy (Dravet, LGS)
- inherited retinal dystrophies (cross-link `.roadmap.disease_sensory`)
- cystic fibrosis (CF) → CFTR modulators
- DMD / SMA (cross-link `.roadmap.disease_musculoskeletal`)
- sickle cell / β-thalassemia (cross-link `.roadmap.disease_hematology`)
- α1-antitrypsin deficiency
- urea cycle disorders / phenylketonuria (PKU) / homocystinuria
- mitochondrial disorders
- metabolic enzyme defects (Pompe / Gaucher / Fabry / MPS-I/II)
- pediatric infectious (RSV / pediatric COVID)
- rare cardiomyopathies (HCM / amyloid)
- progeria (Hutchinson-Gilford)

