## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **rare disease 7000+ entities** = 본 roadmap 의 entry-only scope; per-disease 별도 roadmap 필요 시 개별 land.
2. **gene therapy paradigm 가장 valuable** — Luxturna 2017 / Zolgensma 2019 / Casgevy 2023 / Elevidys 2023 모두 rare disease 첫 FDA gene therapy. VIROCAPSID axis 의 가장 명확 win.
3. **enzyme replacement therapy** — mannose-6-phosphate receptor 기반 lysosome targeting; 단 systemic infusion + life-long.
4. **lonafarnib (Zokinvy 2020)** = first FDA HGPS progeria, average lifespan extension ~2.5 years. quantum-VQE 의 tighter binding 향상 가능.
5. **ASO splice/exon-skipping (Spinraza / eteplirsen)** = nucleic-acid drug paradigm. RIBOZYME axis 의 cross-link, quantum 직접 X.
6. **rare disease economics** = $2-3M one-time gene therapy / $300-750k/yr enzyme replacement. quantum-design 외부 issue.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, rare 임상 의미 한정.

